{"tid":574044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 難抵工傷背痛折磨　運輸工元州仔公園自縊亡","createTime":"2018-02-27T04:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T00:37:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce7c87a1722b3384f810e610511054efd6c869c","tid":574044,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"男子難抵背痛，大埔吊頸身亡。清晨6時許，警方接獲一名姓葉(49歲)女子報案，指其姓謝(57歲)男友在元州仔里1號元州仔公園一株大樹用尼龍繩上吊，警方及消防員趕至，將謝解下，證實他已氣絕身亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後相信事件無可疑，檢走他用作上吊的尼龍繩，以及遺下現場的膠桶及膠櫈等證物。據悉，謝生前任職<span style=\"color: red;\">運輸工，早前因工傷背部疼痛，疑因此萌死念</span>。其多名親友趕抵現場了解，有女親友獲悉噩耗，傷心拭淚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180227/bkn-20180227073302637-0227_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180227%2Fbkn-20180227073302637-0227_00822_001.html&d=MhzRSUmMWK0hiWjdug5Y8Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3f3f19dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180227/bkn-20180227073302637-0227_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"68d6c9619f2f5c9aa3b4224396fd068cba1b6078","tid":574044,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"巨乳人妻未來"},{"pid":"fdb78bb34fd8fae4d9dd6f1345013f1ea1f8ced0","tid":574044,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"返工只會帶來不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a902592b409ec75992370155692baa7c392620d2","tid":574044,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"job get your life<br />\n<br />\nu get none"},{"pid":"50aa6ad0656643f3c530444bfb52ce9d74c9da15","tid":574044,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb78bb34fd8fae4d9dd6f1345013f1ea1f8ced0","tid":574044,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"返工只會帶來不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\