2-27T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8aaa25c0006c0066c1c0ee5481229b95e4a4e010","tid":574044,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:37:53.000Z","msg":"返工=危險??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n路政署外判職員遭撞斃 遺產管理人要求小巴司機賠償<br />\n2018年02月27日 14:43<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/312815-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%92%9E%E6%96%83-%E9%81%BA%E7%94%A2%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com.au%2F172-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%2F312815-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%2596%2583-%25E9%2581%25BA%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%2584%259F%2F&d=MhzRSUmMWK0hiWjdug5Y8Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=dff35f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/312815-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%92%9E%E6%96%83-%E9%81%BA%E7%94%A2%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n路政署任職「IT」孝順仔於前年3月2日在何文田忠孝街橫過馬路時，遭一輛專綫小巴撞倒，頭部重創全身骨折倒臥路中，昏迷送院搶救五句鐘不治。IT男的遺產管理人日前入稟高等法院，要求小巴司機賠償。<br />\n<br />\n34歲死者許志朗為路政署外判職員，主要負責電腦支援工作，他不時會被指派到忠孝街88號何文田政府合署的路政署工作。原告為他的遺產管理人許有斌（譯音），控告合發小巴有限公司及司機余星勳（譯音），入稟狀指，在2015年3月2日早上11時23分，余駕駛專線小巴，沿忠孝街西行至牧愛街交界，撞倒死者。"},{"pid":"9f5ae142023a696ca4fff3aa517175dfcc2d73e0","tid":574044,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:37:40.000Z","msg":"返工危險，申請食老綜算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}